704675f-a.title: Brooklyn: Graham Avenue - Jackson Street
704675f-a.text:
Graham Ave., east side, north of Jackson to Frost Streets. Intersecting
the center of the view is Withers Street. The building at the extreme
right foreground is No. 400. The Synagogue was once the German Evang.
Reformed Church.
March 3, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
